descriptionHTML:
Simple, classy, and elegant. Add a touch of sophistication and glamour to your android wear watch with the Black Marble Watch Face for Watchmaker. Featuring a black marble face, black hour and minute hands, and a gold second hand.

Part of the GlamWear Watch Faces Collection - A collection of watch faces for the modern woman.

NOT A STAND ALONE APP: Black Marble Watch Face requires WatchMaker App to be installed on your phone and android wear watch. WatchMaker is available in the Google Play Store here: http://goo.gl/FMxUfY or actually free from Amazon Underground here: http://amzn.com/B00Y0LHPTY

Compatible with all Android Wear Watches running WatchMaker Pro: LG, Samsung, Huawei, Sony, Asus, Motorola, Fossil, etc. NOT COMPATIBLE WITH TIZEN WATCHES.
